{
  "text": "Apart from these results, it should be noted that our choice of a polynomial function does not imply that this was the most optimal function for immunization. We also tested some other functions including [CITATION_1] bond volatility function with different values of mean reversion and the natural log function. Except for the log function, other functions did not lead to immunization performance similar or better than that of the polynomial functions with low a.",
